---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BiocareValues from '../components/BiocareValues.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import { branches, openBranches, foundations } from '../data/branches';

const openCount = openBranches.length;
const soonCount = branches.filter((b) => b.underConstruction).length;
const foundationBlurb = {
  'St. John Biocare': 'Where it all began in 2011 — our founding foundation, anchored at the Quezon Avenue main center.',
  'Core Renal Center': 'Our sister center, bringing the same standard of dialysis to Makati.',
  'St. Josef Renal Care Foundation': 'Our sister foundation, extending care into Marikina, Bulacan and beyond.',
};
const foundationLogo = {
  'St. John Biocare': '/images/logos/logo-sjbdc.webp',
  'Core Renal Center': '/images/logos/corerenalcare-logo.webp',
  'St. Josef Renal Care Foundation': '/images/logos/stjosef-logo.webp',
};
---
<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="St. John Biocare is a SEC-registered foundation born from one family's experience of kidney failure — our story, mission, values and leadership." image="/images/og/og-about.jpg">
  <PageHero
    image="/images/heroes/about-hero.webp"
    alt="An adult son resting a reassuring hand on his elderly father's shoulder, both smiling"
    eyebrow="Our story"
    title="A foundation, born from a real family story."
    subtitle="Not a corporate chain, but a foundation — born from one son's love for his mother, and a refusal to let excellent dialysis be a privilege of the few."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px" class:list={['stack']}>
      <p>
        It began in a family, in a hard season. A son watched his mother face end-stage renal
        disease and walked every step of it beside her — the hospital, the fear, the slow new
        rhythm of dialysis that would now shape her weeks. And in the middle of it, he saw
        something he would never forget: just how much truly <em>excellent</em> care can change,
        not only for the patient in the chair, but for the whole family holding its breath around
        her.
      </p>
      <p>
        He also saw how rare that care could be — and he refused to accept it. When his mother
        moved to outpatient dialysis, what the family found at existing centers convinced him of
        one thing: someone had to do this better. So, with a lifelong friend and partner, he
        decided that someone would be them. The idea grew from something simple and stubborn —
        compassion, and an unwavering grit for excellence.
      </p>
      <p>
        One conviction drove them, and still does: world-class hemodialysis should never be a
        privilege of the few. It should reach the many — ordinary Filipino families — without ever
        asking them to trade their safety for what they can afford. Not someday. Here, and now.
      </p>
      <p>
        On <strong>June 28, 2011</strong>, that resolve became real: St. John Biocare was
        registered with the SEC, and its first clinic opened in Quezon City on
        <strong>October 16, 2011</strong>. We were built as a non-stock <strong>foundation</strong>
        on purpose — it means we answer to a mission, not to shareholders. What started as one
        family's promise is now a growing network of centers, and we are only getting started.
      </p>

      <figure style="margin:28px 0 4px">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/why-we-exist.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img src="/images/why-we-exist.jpg" width="1600" height="800" loading="lazy"
               alt="An illustrated three-panel story: a son at his mother's side during dialysis, the resolve to build better care, and a warm, excellent dialysis center"
               style="width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);display:block" />
        </picture>
      </figure>

      <div class="notice">
        <strong>Our care philosophy</strong>
        <p style="margin:.4rem 0 0">
          “The St. John Biocare Way is to put the patient first… we must see the world through
          the eyes of our patients and their families.” We call the people we serve
          <strong>client-patients</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BY THE NUMBERS -->
  <section class="section stats">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats__grid">
        <div><strong>15 years</strong><span>of dialysis care since 2011</span></div>
        <div><strong>{openCount} centers</strong><span>open across Metro Manila &amp; Bulacan</span></div>
        <div><strong>{soonCount} more</strong><span>under construction, opening this year</span></div>
        <div><strong>{foundations.length} foundations</strong><span>one growing family of care</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR JOURNEY -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our journey</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:26px">From one clinic to a growing network.</h2>
      <ol class="timeline">
        <li>
          <p class="yr">June 2011</p>
          <h3>Registered as a foundation</h3>
          <p>On June 28, 2011, St. John Biocare was registered with the SEC as a <strong>non-stock,
          non-profit foundation</strong> — built to answer to a mission, not to shareholders.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p class="yr">October 2011</p>
          <h3>The first center opens</h3>
          <p>Our very first dialysis clinic opened its doors in Quezon City on October 16, 2011, on
          Quezon Avenue — still our main center today.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p class="yr">2012 – 2013</p>
          <h3>A second center joins the family — Marikina</h3>
          <p>In September 2012, we acquired the <strong>St. Pio Dialysis Center Foundation</strong> in
          Marikina and rechristened it <strong>St. John Biocare Dialysis Center – Marikina</strong>,
          formally opening its doors on January 25, 2013.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p class="yr">The years since</p>
          <h3>Growing into a network</h3>
          <p>Center by center, the promise spread across Metro Manila — and our sister foundations,
          <strong>Core Renal Center</strong> and <strong>St. Josef Renal Care</strong>, joined the family.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p class="yr">Today</p>
          <h3>Fifteen years, and counting</h3>
          <p>Fifteen years on, <strong>{openCount} centers</strong> are open across Metro Manila and
          Bulacan, with <strong>{soonCount} more</strong> under construction — among the country's pioneers
          of free-standing dialysis care.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p class="yr">Ahead</p>
          <h3>Only getting started</h3>
          <p>The mission has not changed: excellent, honest dialysis for every family. We are only
          getting started.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR NETWORK -->
  <section class="section section--sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="center" style="margin-bottom:30px;max-width:720px;margin-inline:auto">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our network</p>
        <h2>Three foundations, one family of care.</h2>
        <p class="lead" style="margin-inline:auto">St. John Biocare grew into a network of sister
        foundations — each independent, all holding to the same standard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        {foundations.map((f) => {
          const open = openBranches.filter((b) => b.foundation === f);
          const soon = branches.filter((b) => b.foundation === f && b.underConstruction);
          return (
            <div class="card">
              <img src={foundationLogo[f]} alt={`${f} logo`} width="72" height="72" loading="lazy"
                   style="width:72px;height:72px;object-fit:contain;display:block;margin-bottom:12px" />
              <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem">{f}</h3>
              <p class="muted" style="margin:.2rem 0 .8rem">{foundationBlurb[f]}</p>
              <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:1.1rem;line-height:1.7">
                {open.map((b) => <li>{b.name} <span class="muted" style="font-size:.85rem">· {b.area}</span></li>)}
              </ul>
              {soon.length > 0 && (
                <p class="muted" style="font-size:.85rem;margin:.7rem 0 0">+ {soon.length} more opening this year</p>
              )}
            </div>
          );
        })}
      </div>
      <div class="center" style="margin-top:26px">
        <a href="/centers" class="btn btn--primary">See all our centers</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT -->
  <section class="section section--mist">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px">
      <p class="eyebrow">What makes us different</p>
      <h2>Being a foundation means the patient always wins.</h2>
      <p>Because we answer to a mission and not to shareholders, every peso goes back into care — and into
      the standards others quietly skip. Well-established medicines, water purified twice by <strong>dual-pass
      reverse osmosis</strong>, machines calibrated by their own makers, and a bar set by both Philippine
      <strong>and international best practice</strong>. Excellence is not our marketing. It is the whole
      reason we exist.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:18px"><a href="/services" class="btn btn--primary">See the standards we hold</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--sand">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:900px">
      <div class="center" style="margin-bottom:34px;max-width:640px;margin-inline:auto">
        <p class="eyebrow">What drives us</p>
        <h2>Our vision &amp; mission.</h2>
        <p class="lead" style="margin-inline:auto">The future we are working toward — and what we do every day to get there.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--2">
        <div class="card vm-card">
          <span class="vm-tag vm-tag--vision">Vision</span>
          <p class="vm-def">A vision is the future we want to help create — where we are headed.</p>
          <p class="vm-quote">“To become the leading free-standing dialysis center and diagnostic facility in providing exemplary service to patients with end-stage renal disease.”</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card vm-card">
          <span class="vm-tag vm-tag--mission">Mission</span>
          <p class="vm-def">A mission is what we do every day, and how, to make that future real.</p>
          <p class="vm-quote">“To provide the best-quality expert clinical care through state-of-the-art, innovative and affordable hemodialysis treatments and diagnostics manned by outstanding and compassionate personnel, responsive to the needs of our patients.”</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="center" style="margin-bottom:30px">
        <p class="eyebrow">What we stand for</p>
        <h2>The BIOCARE values.</h2>
      </div>
      <BiocareValues />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .stats { background: var(--forest); }
  .stats__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .stats__grid strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 2rem; color: #fff; line-height: 1.1; }
  .stats__grid span { color: #cfe6d6; font-size: .95rem; }
  @media (max-width: 820px) { .stats__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px 16px; } }

  .timeline { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; position: relative; }
  .timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 7px; top: 8px; bottom: 8px; width: 2px; background: var(--border); }
  .timeline li { position: relative; padding: 0 0 26px 40px; }
  .timeline li:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }
  .timeline li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 4px; width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--life); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--cream); }
  .timeline .yr { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; color: var(--forest); font-size: .9rem; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .04em; }
  .timeline h3 { margin: .1rem 0 .35rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .timeline li > p:last-child { margin: 0; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  .vm-card { padding: 32px 30px; }
  .vm-tag { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; font-size: .82rem; color: #fff; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .vm-tag--vision { background: var(--forest); }
  .vm-tag--mission { background: var(--crimson); }
  .vm-def { margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: .92rem; }
  .vm-quote { margin: 0; font-family: var(--font-head); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--forest); }
</style>
